 In version      : 04.12
 Location        : Startup
 Situation       : Starting VideoMaxe up from Workbench with VM: not
                   assigned.
 Error           : VideoMaxe will not automatically assign VM: to the
                   current directory.
 Ok since        : 04.20
 Notes           : Did look for the cli-structure only...

@ENDNODE

